# Development Protocol

This project uses the Meta-Prompts protocol for AI-assisted software development.

If `.build/` does not exist: read `[META_PROMPTS_PATH]/BOOTSTRAP.md` and follow the initialization sequence before writing any code.

If `.build/` exists: read `.build/AGENT.md`, `.build/SPEC.md`, and `.build/BUILD_LOG.md` in that order, then resume from the last log entry.

Never write application code before the Phase 1 specification is approved by the human.

Meta-prompts location: [META_PROMPTS_PATH]/
